OL,5, Energy regulator Ofgem says suppliers  
OL,6, must be accurate with bills and deal   
OL,7, quickly with mistakes, following a row 
OL,8, involving artist Sir Grayson Perry.    
OL,10,FThe Turner Prize-winning artist        
OL,11,Fcriticised EDF after receiving a stack 
OL,12,Fof bills that added up to #39,000.     
OL,14,FThe company said that problems with    
OL,15,Fbills could happen occasionally, but   
OL,16,Fthere were no fundamental, broader     
OL,17,Fissues with how its system was working.
OL,19,FOfgem said it would not hesitate to act
OL,20,Fif any suppliers were breaking rules.  
